            <formatted-text>
              <run fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Arial,sans-serif' fontsize='7'>⦿ </run>
              <run fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='7'>Nearly two-thirds of submitted claims remain pending or rejected, indicating potential opportunities to review claim processing efficiency.</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Arial,sans-serif' fontsize='7'>⦿ </run>
              <run fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='7'>High-severity claims account for nearly half of total claim volume and should receive enhanced monitoring.</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Arial,sans-serif' fontsize='7'>⦿ </run>
              <run fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='7'>Health policies generate the largest claim payout, suggesting further review of pricing and underwriting strategy.</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            </formatted-text>
